			<pb n="20" />
			<p rend="center"> A REBUS <emph>on the late</emph> Mr Henry Purcells <emph>Name by</emph> Mr
				Tomlinson <emph>Set by</emph> Mr I Lenton </p>
			<notatedMusic rend="mei" source="rebus.mei" />
			<lg type="stanza">
				<l>Galli marita par tritico seges,</l>
				<l>Prœnomen est ejus, dat chromati leges</l>
				<l>Intrat cognome, blanditiis Cati,</l>
				<l>Exit Eremi in Œdibus stati,</l>
				<l>Expertum effectum emnes admirentur</l>
				<l>Quid merent Poetœ? ut bene calcentur.</l>
			</lg>
		</body>
	</text>
